* List of gaps in bib number sequence
*  Purpose:         Identifies missing bib numbers in your sequence to ensure all runners are entered.
*    When to use:   During race setup (1-2 days prior) or for final checks right before the start.
*    How it works:  Scans the database for gaps and saves the report to "c:\tmp\bib_gaps.txt". Open this file in Notepad++ or your preferred text editor to review the results.
*

missing numbers     Bib
Destination         %temp_dir%\bib_gaps.txt